Telkom has unveiled its Deal of the Month for February. The deal includes a Huawei E5573 MiFi router, 5GB of anytime data, and 10GB of Night Surfer data (midnight to 07:00) for R149 per month for 24 months. The deal is available on a Smart One-Rate plan, which offers a flat rate of 15c per MB. The Huawei LTE MiFi router features a 1,500mAh battery and can connect up to 10 devices simultaneously. 